---
title: Cannellini Bean and Chorizo Stew with parsley and chilli flake garnish
description: This hearty chorizo and bean stew filled with velvety leeks makes the perfect midweek meal. You'll find it's super simple to prepare and the slight spice from the chorizo means this dish will be warming in more ways than one!
